WEBVTT

19:55.850 --> 19:56.780 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

19:56.310 --> 19:58.100 line:80%
When you agreed to marry into my family,

19:56.800 --> 19:59.310 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

19:58.630 --> 20:00.000 line:80%
we were already even.

20:00.590 --> 20:01.530 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

20:01.550 --> 20:03.900 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

20:01.720 --> 20:03.180 line:80%
You want to be even with me?

20:04.700 --> 20:08.590 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪
